name: The Phoenix
description: “A mythical bird of great beauty fabled to live 500 or 600 years in the Arabian wilderness, to burn itself on a funeral pyre, and to rise from its ashes in the freshness of youth and live through another cycle of years: often an emblem of immortality or of reborn idealism or hope” (from Dictionary)  This is an actual cloud photo I captured before the winds dissipated it.  @fotochad
